titleInfo.title: Walls v. Corporation for National and Community Service
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER ON INITIAL REVIEW - The plaintiff's Motion (Application) for Leave to Proceed IFP 15, and the Motion that the Marshal Serve Summons 16 are both granted. The Clerk of Court shall send the plaintiff a copy of filing no. 12 and this order, as well as 3 Form USM-285s, to be completed in accordance with FRCP 4(i). Upon receipt of the summons and 285 forms, the clerk shall forward the forms, together with copies of the Amended Complaint to the US Marshal. The defendant shall answer or otherwise respond to the Amended Complaint within the appropriate period. Signed by Magistrate Judge F. A. Gossett on 7/21/2006. (Order (filing 12), 3 blank summons and 285 Forms sent as directed)(KBJ)
